Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.46,0:00:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛逝的秒針 閃耀的流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.26,0:00:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今社會人心貧瘠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.01,0:00:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南的推理是一帖良藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.92,0:00:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事件是隱藏在繃帶中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.88,0:00:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.50,0:00:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.49,0:00:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.60,0:00:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.96,0:01:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舉行長門集團會長的生日派對時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.25,0:01:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次女康江小姐的丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.17,0:01:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明先生在樓下的房間遭人襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.73,0:01:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走到陽台讓我們看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.12,0:01:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是臉上纏著繃帶的長子 秀臣先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.72,0:01:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕到樓下的房間的時候已經太遲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明先生被外面欄杆的尖刺刺穿身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.52,0:02:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當場死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.52,0:02:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發兩天後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.28,0:02:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著秀臣先生投池自殺的遺體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.34,0:02:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺書也隨之曝光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.18,0:02:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也間接證明了他是那件命案的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.44,0:02:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我認為那封遺書有太多的疑點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.41,0:02:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.32,0:02:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣先生在案發之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.19,0:02:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已經被殺害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.71,0:02:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名家連續慘死事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.72,0:02:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你說都沒有人出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.75,0:02:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確沒有人離開這個屋子到外面去過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在傍晚之前都進到屋子裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.11,0:02:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你爸爸還特別交待過我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.57,0:02:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.03,0:02:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那天我們離開玄關的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.45,0:02:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是跟你一起趕到屍體所在的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.70,0:02:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一兩分鐘的時間而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.32,0:02:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.52,0:02:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣先生從另外一邊繞到水池來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.09,0:03:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳到水池裡面自盡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.71,0:03:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要說有誰出去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有已經死亡的光明先生而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.97,0:03:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光…光明先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.91,0:03:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.03,0:03:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是在九點半的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.85,0:03:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那個時候他說要去找秀臣先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻看到他到處在找東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.53,0:03:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是到院子裡的樹叢裡 就是跑到水池周圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.75,0:03:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近秀臣先生有什麼不一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.49,0:03:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.81,0:03:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你們有沒有什麼印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.91,0:03:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.80,0:03:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實他平常就不是很愛說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.25,0:03:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.40,0:03:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發那天還有案發之前的那天 他都比平常吃得要多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.62,0:03:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連他平常不吃的甜點都吃了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他平常連早餐都不吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.04,0:03:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還嚇了一跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.43,0:03:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那秀臣先生平常臉上一直都包著那個繃帶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.99,0:03:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.82,0:03:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每隔三天他的妹妹康江小姐都會定期幫他換繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.60,0:03:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得她最後幫他換繃帶 剛好是在案發的前兩天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.59,0:04:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天前家裡突然少了一張床單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳確定數過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.44,0:04:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤 你過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.36,0:04:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.51,0:04:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明先生和康江小姐他們房間的陽臺下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.78,0:04:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被什麼東西敲打過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.88,0:04:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.11,0:04:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是光明先生被推落跌下的陽臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也有相同的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這邊跟那邊不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的印子要比那邊多得多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.43,0:04:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信子小姐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.16,0:04:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.21,0:04:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤 這樣好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會被誤認成小偷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.20,0:04:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪放得了心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.38,0:04:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電…電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.76,0:05:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是信子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.62,0:05:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子還挺鎮定的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.46,0:05:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天前妳不是喝了好多酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話到我家答錄機裡面留話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.54,0:05:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天前什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 妳都忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在晚上十點之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概有三十分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一分鐘都沒停過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳如果不記得的話就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.92,0:05:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.77,0:05:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說是兩天前的十點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.91,0:05:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就剛好是案發的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.15,0:05:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣至少可以確定從陽臺上把臉露出來的那個包繃帶的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.34,0:05:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能是信子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠做到這件事的就只有秀臣先生本人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.23,0:05:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.06,0:05:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去秀臣先生的房間裡找找看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.90,0:05:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡全是書嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小說家的房間好像都是這麼亂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.79,0:05:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己還不是把人家的房間搞亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.77,0:05:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是電話答錄機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.51,0:06:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面好像還有留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.28,0:06:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.15,0:06:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們聽聽看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.75,0:06:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是《文藝時代》的山田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.33,0:06:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次交稿的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.76,0:06:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就訂在明天中午一點鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是在老地方見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.80,0:06:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十月三十一號下午一點二十八分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十月三十一號這天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是案發的前一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.58,0:06:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是山田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.69,0:06:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經到了我們常去的咖啡店了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.23,0:06:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十一月一號下午三點零四分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.60,0:06:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是山田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.77,0:06:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經等了六個小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你是不會來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.69,0:06:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天我先回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.08,0:06:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 秀臣先生這個時候就已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.73,0:06:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方估算他的死亡時間明明…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.21,0:06:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.43,0:06:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好有個方法可以這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且能夠做到這件事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有那個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.76,0:07:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.57,0:07:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個東西應該還在囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們的推理沒有錯的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.41,0:07:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.22,0:07:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沾滿泥巴的床單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.63,0:07:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡還有一個泳帽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部 你怎麼在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.70,0:07:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把日向小姐的鋼筆還給人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.31,0:07:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 我忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們回去了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天都已經黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.77,0:07:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在幾點鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.21,0:07:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差十分鐘就七點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 店一定還開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.80,0:07:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭大姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我把這些買回來好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 信子小姐正上方的那間房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.71,0:07:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道現在是誰在用嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.96,0:07:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是我在用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 一個小時之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.66,0:07:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家到妳的房間去好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.40,0:08:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼暫時就留在我這邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.32,0:08:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.12,0:08:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要叫小五郎叔叔快點過來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經用麻醉槍讓毛利大叔睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.66,0:08:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們推理需要用到的東西現在也全買齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的推理很完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.74,0:08:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們卻忘了一件最重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.22,0:08:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.78,0:08:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.71,0:08:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都把這個給忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.25,0:08:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在幾點鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.01,0:08:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七點四十分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過十分鐘大家都要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.44,0:08:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的什麼都沒有注意到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.32,0:08:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是關東的名偵探耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.55,0:08:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.64,0:08:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是關西的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.22,0:08:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.69,0:08:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.06,0:08:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 我們就照原定計劃在十分鐘之後開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.89,0:09:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.95,0:09:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有沒有殺過人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.22,0:09:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來了 服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.70,0:09:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我們來有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.17,0:09:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.26,0:09:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家到這裡的人其實是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.32,0:09:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.69,0:09:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已經知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將光明先生殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.85,0:09:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再將秀臣先生沉進水池裡的兇手是誰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.85,0:09:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將光明先生殺死的人可是秀臣先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.97,0:09:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後他自己才在水池裡面服毒自殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封遺書上面留的字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.67,0:09:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過鑑定之後也確實是秀臣先生的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電…電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.81,0:09:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.59,0:09:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在請你把話筒拿起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.60,0:09:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 這整起案件就會在大家眼前重演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.24,0:09:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是光明先生掉到欄杆上死亡的慘劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.94,0:10:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.85,0:10:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 是我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 是服部啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.78,0:10:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.79,0:10:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人把燈關掉了 手上還拿著刀子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.31,0:10:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.49,0:10:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你們下面的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.53,0:10:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出了什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.67,0:10:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.55,0:10:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 先到下面去救他要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.99,0:10:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是藉此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.45,0:10:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將大家引開這間房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是要隱藏之後在這個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.24,0:10:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生的更恐怖的行徑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發當時用電話引起騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.01,0:11:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有拿著刀子綁上繃帶故意露出臉讓大家看到兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是光明先生為了嫁禍給秀臣先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.23,0:11:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由他一個人自己演出的一場獨角戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.06,0:11:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.37,0:11:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手身上明明沾了光明先生噴出來的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.71,0:11:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且光明先生的屍體上也有刀傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.78,0:11:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傷口其實是光明先生自己事先割傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.73,0:11:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繃帶上的血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.73,0:11:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他用針筒抽自己的血後再噴到繃帶上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.49,0:11:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於繃帶和帽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是秀臣先生用過的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.94,0:11:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了不讓自己的頭髮粘上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.82,0:11:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先戴了一頂泳帽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.82,0:11:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,針管跟泳帽實在光明先生房間裡發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.58,0:11:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是最後被殺的還是光明先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.69,0:11:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他為什麼要這麼做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.72,0:11:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.79,0:11:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的目的就是為了殺害長門會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.04,0:11:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他的共犯這個時候已經讓會長睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.68,0:12:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那個共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.13,0:12:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在將大家引到下面的房間的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門光明再上來將長門會長殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.85,0:12:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再回到那個房間裡面換裝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.99,0:12:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.93,0:12:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有想到居然會被這名共犯給殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.78,0:12:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.66,0:12:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟會長一起留在房間裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向幸小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.05,0:12:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.07,0:12:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.58,0:12:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.53,0:12:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想光明先生當時一定非常驚訝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.67,0:12:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本房裡應該只會有會長一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳竟然會留在陽臺那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.33,0:12:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且竟然還把他從那裡推了下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.26,0:12:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果真是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.49,0:12:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光明先生應該跟著刀子一起掉下去才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在刀子被帶上房間之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.82,0:12:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就跟帽子和繃帶一起被丟到外面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.21,0:12:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明先生原本就計畫利用上衣中的風箏線將會長給勒死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.94,0:12:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.84,0:12:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向小姐的目標只有光明先生一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.41,0:12:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是她完全沒有想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被殺的光明先生也耍了詭計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個上面有鉤子的繩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這點非常的簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.50,0:13:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明先生將繩子倒拉上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.57,0:13:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鉤子的另外一邊綁上重物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後鉤在下面陽臺上的欄杆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.06,0:13:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 只要把另外一頭綁上重物放下去之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.17,0:13:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重物在到達陽臺下面以後就會自己停下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據就是 這種被重物打到過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.38,0:13:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就出現在會長房間下面的光明先生房間的陽台外側
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及在這個房間下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信子小姐房間的陽臺外側
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.25,0:13:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想日向小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.59,0:13:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在案發的前一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定曾經試過這個計畫的可能性吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.33,0:13:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為會長聽到了這個聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.63,0:13:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.95,0:13:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也同時聽到好像有人在走廊上面跑步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個跑步聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.64,0:13:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是日向小姐為了計算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.18,0:13:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從光明先生的房間到存放備用鑰匙的倉庫之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.12,0:13:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往返的時間所發出的腳步聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 這個是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向小姐在案發的前一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已經著手準備的殺人計畫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.56,0:14:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說秀臣先生也是被她殺的囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那遺書怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.59,0:14:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才說過了 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.96,0:14:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向小姐的目標只有光明先生一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.55,0:14:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封遺書是案發的前一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.85,0:14:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就已經自殺的秀臣先生留給日向小姐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發的前一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我判斷 日向小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.45,0:14:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許就是發現了秀臣先生在房裡自殺之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.57,0:14:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才想到要進行這一整套的殺人計畫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.46,0:14:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於秀臣先生的預估死亡時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.92,0:14:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢察官明明已經確認了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.57,0:14:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為土的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.13,0:14:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果將屍體掩埋在土裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讓它接觸空氣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.92,0:14:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體腐爛的速度是正常的八分之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想日向小姐也許是請光明先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.19,0:14:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先用被單將秀臣先生包起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個再一起趁著大清早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷地把他埋到水池旁邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.48,0:15:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為水池旁邊本來就有很多為了種樹所挖的洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.65,0:15:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算再多幾個洞 誰也不會注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.56,0:15:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又是誰把遺體丟進水池裡面的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.54,0:15:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是光明先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在案發之前把他挖了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.33,0:15:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才丟進水池裡面去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他謊稱要去找秀臣先生的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.33,0:15:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 案發當天秀臣先生明明還在屋子裡頭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.54,0:15:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.14,0:15:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你所看到的只是偽裝成秀臣先生的日向小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.90,0:15:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是光明先生罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.82,0:15:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家只要聽過秀臣先生房裡的電話答錄機就會非常清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.71,0:15:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實秀臣先生在案發的前一天就已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.07,0:15:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼光明先生會按照日向小姐的計畫行事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.81,0:15:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也許是日向小姐曾經對他這麼說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 你就可以得到會長的寶座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也可以將所有罪名都推到秀臣先生身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.06,0:15:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個兩全其美的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.69,0:15:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向小姐曾經被秀臣先生從火場撿回一條命來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.29,0:16:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼可能會讓救命恩人背這種罪名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.05,0:16:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們根本沒有證據 不要亂說好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在幾點鐘了 日向小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.24,0:16:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你現在問這個幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.20,0:16:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 你的手錶哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.67,0:16:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是今天剛好忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 妳不是忘記戴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是妳根本就不能戴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.22,0:16:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為手錶的錶帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.56,0:16:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就在那個時候被弄壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想妳在把光明先生從陽臺上推下去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就緊抓著妳的錶帶 沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.41,0:16:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想如果被他拉掉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.37,0:16:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻錶就會掉落在命案現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳情急之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用身上帶著的某個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.83,0:16:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往光明先生的右手背上刺了下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.30,0:16:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個東西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.03,0:16:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.67,0:16:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鋼筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.22,0:16:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.34,0:16:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她靈機一動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用嘴巴把筆套咬開 刺了下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.18,0:16:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是她父親留給她的那個遺物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.73,0:17:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你們怎麼會連這種事情都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我曾經打開過筆套一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.39,0:17:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我本來想寫字的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到筆尖卻分叉得很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.67,0:17:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這支筆是她從火災現場帶出來的遺物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能會讓筆尖變成那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.85,0:17:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.07,0:17:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是日向小姐為什麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半是因為那場火災吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.09,0:17:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據我們兩個的推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.43,0:17:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們懷疑二十年前引起那場火災的人恐怕就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣先生和光明先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.33,0:17:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣先生之所以一直沒有醫治臉上的傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.25,0:17:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許就是因為他在懊悔當年所犯的罪過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那封遺書還有下文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他把這整件事完全寫清楚的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.67,0:17:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一切就說得通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.95,0:17:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.17,0:17:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說她是為了替她在火災中喪生的父母報仇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.85,0:17:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 還有件事我們還是不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.26,0:17:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼要故意激怒信子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓警方發現秀臣先生在水池裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該是妳故意的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.54,0:18:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣放著不管 總有一天警方還是會發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.59,0:18:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不希望再讓他泡在那麼冰冷的水池裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.77,0:18:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.67,0:18:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.46,0:18:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個瓶子裡面已經裝滿了汽油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.61,0:18:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.55,0:18:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位偵探先生說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.20,0:18:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺書裡面的確把火災的事情全部都寫了進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.80,0:18:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不能原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.81,0:18:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們做了這種事情 光明還能無恥地苟活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.50,0:18:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且秀臣他竟然一直沒把這件事情告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.48,0:18:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.53,0:18:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.29,0:18:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻已經無可救藥地愛上他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.43,0:18:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個衝進火場把我救出來的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.82,0:18:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個一直鼓勵我讓我走出陰霾的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.54,0:18:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.85,0:19:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還接受我求婚的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是秀臣已經不在這世上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又變成孤單一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.51,0:19:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得快點到他身邊才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.72,0:19:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.93,0:19:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.61,0:19:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個瓶子裡面只有水而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.24,0:19:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.35,0:19:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.05,0:19:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要點火就這麼簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.64,0:19:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的火卻點不著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.23,0:19:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.75,0:19:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實就讓她那樣死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.29,0:19:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是一件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.97,0:19:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們偵探把兇手逼到盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果最後就讓他們自我了結的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和殺人犯有什麼不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這些話還真是刺耳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.12,0:20:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話也只有你這種完美主義者說得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.54,0:20:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上根本沒有哪個人是完美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾經殺過一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那一個人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.77,0:20:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我想那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.29,0:20:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能夠解救日向小姐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.38,0:20:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別這樣 日向小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.22,0:20:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果跟著秀臣去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.04,0:20:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就實在太傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.03,0:20:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的母親從前可不是這樣的一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.36,0:20:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又知道什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就不知道我媽媽是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.35,0:20:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.35,0:20:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你一直帶著的那支鋼筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.96,0:20:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我在小學的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.88,0:20:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給當時要轉學的你母親的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.99,0:21:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳似乎把它看成了是你父親留給你的遺物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.72,0:21:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會要求妳原諒秀臣所犯下的罪過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.06,0:21:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳還這麼年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生還長得很呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得為秀臣好好地活下去才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.79,0:21:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想妳母親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.97,0:21:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定也會希望這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.74,0:22:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.34,0:22:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來會長的初戀情人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.02,0:22:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是日向小姐的媽媽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.58,0:22:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.84,0:23:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以會長當時才會為了保護她才對我們撒那個謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.10,0:23:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.35,0:23:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來他騙我們說日向小姐一直在他身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.20,0:23:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想為他的兒子贖罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.81,0:23:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來還有這種用意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.93,0:23:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想會長之所以想見他的初戀情人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.90,0:23:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在日向小姐身上看到了他初戀情人的影子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.72,0:23:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.87,0:23:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就注意到了這件事卻不跟我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.99,0:23:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又說工藤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.69,0:23:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的工藤難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.66,0:23:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.32,0:23:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦 囉嗦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.32,0:23:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}工藤跟囉嗦日文發音相近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.92,0:23:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他一直問我案子的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.61,0:23:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會說他囉嗦的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.04,0:23:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是大阪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.93,0:23:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要裝蒜我可是日本第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.28,0:23:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎菜 你在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.12,0:23:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰的車子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.87,0:23:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說椎菜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.58,0:23:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少回個話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.61,0:24:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小南她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.77,0:24:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小南她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.95,0:24:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被綁架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.56,0:24:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.89,0:24:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢在我面前綁人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.64,0:24:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.01,0:24:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當紅藝人綁架事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.38,0:24:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.71,0:24:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TWO-MIX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.08,0:24:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回是那當紅團體登場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.10,0:24:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你跟TWO-MIX有什麼關係啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.11,0:24:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃！
